high_descs: Head left to the kitchen to reach the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and head to the pink table in the living room.
Put the potato on the pink table next to the book.
anns.task_desc: Put the hot potato on the table.

high_descs: Exit the room then  turn right and walk down the hallway and into the kitchen
Pick up the potato from the sink
Turn left and open the microwave
Heat the potato in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk into the living room
Set the potato down on the pink table
anns.task_desc: Heat the potato and place it on the pink table

high_descs: Walk out the room turn right down hall to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Go to and open up the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave, close, then open and take it out.
Go to the low table behind you.
Place the potato on table to right of the book.
anns.task_desc: Go to sink with potato, take it out microwave, take it to the table in the next room.

high_descs: walk through the hallway and go to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
walk over to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave, heat it up, and then remove it.
take it to the tvstand in the living room.
Put the potato on top of the tvstand.
anns.task_desc: Get a potato from one place and put it at the TVStand.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward, turn right, walk down the hallway, turn left, walk up to the kitchen sink and stop.
Pick up the potato out of the sink.
Turn to your microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato in, turn the microwave on, and then take the potato out when the microwave stops.
Turn left, walk forward, go into the living room, and turn left stopping in front of the tvstand.
Put the potato down on top of the tvstand.
anns.task_desc: Cook the potato then put it down on top of the TVStand.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the potato from the sink.
Turn left and go near the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave oven.
Then take the tvstand out and go near the side table.
Put the potato on the tvstand.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the TVStand.
